  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0db0\u0db1\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 50 \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dda \u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I put my personal wealth into 50 million people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dhammika Perera, Minister of Investment Promotion said that they will spend Rs. 50 million of their personal wealth on behalf of the people on a monthly basis through the new Ministry.",
        "The Minister said this while participating in a 360 talk show on Derana TV last night.",
        "\"If I call for tenders and go to work, it will take a long time. I took over the ministry assuming that I would invest my personal money of Rs. 50 million a month.",
        "I sat in this chair with such a budget reserved for me. I do not expect government money. I put my personal money into 50 million people a month. I'm ready to go and learn in this chair. \""
      ],
